{"tid":40294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"綠茶杏仁脆餅","createTime":"2016-12-15T06:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T06:27:23.000Z","uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bfc68653fabe1004b0a6c1a37c4a1b5d8e51ffb","tid":40294,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:23:44.000Z","msg":"尋日貼左紫薯, 今日唔爭在貼埋綠茶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3463.jpg?w=1462\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3463.jpg%3Fw%3D1462&h=aa454437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料 (約35塊)<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3429.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3429.jpg&d=9emy94v%2FTJBH2%2FQLYpxy8QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b85439e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3429.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n全蛋\t1隻<br />\n低筋麵粉\t180g<br />\n糖霜\t75g<br />\n鹽\t1小撮<br />\n無鹽牛油\t90g<br />\n綠茶粉\t5g<br />\n杏仁片\t50g"},{"pid":"f45b6b2f8e9079314968531f05ac8c5baa57cb0e","tid":40294,"uid":4456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"1) 雞蛋打勻備用<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3430.jpg&h=3290e281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 無鹽牛油置室溫軟化後, 加入糖霜拌成忌廉狀<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3431.jpg&h=fe3ae21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 之後加入綠茶粉及鹽拌勻<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3432.jpg&h=70b5e5fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4) 雞蛋分2-3 次加入, 拌至完全融合<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3434.jpg&h=b6daec7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) 篩入麵粉拌成麵團<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3435.jpg&h=7a70ece5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6) 之後加入杏仁片拌勻, 隨喜好搓成長方型或圓型<br />\n<img src=\"http://vlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com/2016/05/img_3439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecookingdotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F05%2Fimg_3439.jpg&h=2ddff9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=9emy94v%2FTJBH2%2FQLYpxy8QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=69872b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vlovecooking.com/</a> <br />\nblog: <a href=\"https://vlovecooking.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvlovecooking.com%2F&d=9emy94v%2FTJBH2%2FQLYpxy8QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=1b69e949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vlovecooking.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}